description: Enjoy this super quick fried rice the whole family will love, ready in 10 minutes!
name: Fast Pork Fried Rice Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 250 g Woolworths Simply Stir-Fry Vegetable Superfoods
45 g Five tastes stir fry shot

recipeInstructions.text: Add cooked rice and stir to coat in remaining sesame oil. Add stir fry shot and toss to combine. Spoon into shallow bowls and serve.
